name: PixelDrop_LeakingPipe_320x320
description: Leaking Pipe. PixelBlock series started 2011. The series strips animation and graphics back to basics. They draw on Minimalism & early computer games. This series uses black & white, with a base resolution of 3x3 pixels. This output: 320x320res. There are variations in speed: slow & sluggish to HYPER fast.(2021)
